       <h5><span>Editors' Picks</span></h5> 
       <div class="teaser" data-vr-contentbox=""> 
        <h3> <a href="http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/hockey/youth-hockey-team-escapes-roof-collapse-rink-article-1.2134084"> Youth hockey team escapes roof collapse at rink</a> </h3> 
